description: - Monochrome - 600 x 600 dpi Print - Plain Paper Print - Desktop - 100 ppm Mono Print - 600 sheets Standard Input Capacity - 275000 pages per month - Automatic Duplex Print - LCD - Ethernet - Wireless LAN - USB Imagine being able to print up to 100 black and white pages per minute without reloading the paper tray. With the HLS7000DN you can do it.If your work group has high-volume print demands you’ll be looking for speed reliability and cost efficiency. This printer delivers.It is cost-effective – printing 30000 sheets from a single super high yield ink cartridge and consuming approximately one sixth (16 percent) of the power of similar printers.It is also extremely reliable — a low touch machine which means it doesn’t jam or break down.And it has high paper capacity: expandable to 2100 sheets with the optional additional paper trays. (With optional paper trays expanding paper capacity to 2100 sheets if needed) HLS7000DN | High speed inkjet printerFunctionsPrintConnectivityNetwork / USBPrinter TypeBlack & White InkjetDouble Sided Print/Scan/CopyPrint onlyPrint SpeedUp to 100ppm (black & white)Ink/TonerHC05BK 30000 pages @ 5% coveragePaper SizeA4 Letter B5(/JIS) A5 A5(Long Edge) Exective Legal FolioDimensions (WxDxH) With Carton665x642x729mm 52kg
